      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASTRAL STRIDE (10) produced a very good effort here last week when chasing along the sprint lane for second and just 1.2 metres from the winner. Draws on the back row but will be peaking now so with even luck she can go one better. FRENCH STREET (1) came from a much wider barrier for fourth last week, beaten 4.5 metres. Had won three of her previous four outings, two of them at this circuit and distance. Should get her chance from this favourable starting position. KYLEIGH (3) won here three back and has placed in both outings since, beaten only 1.6m last week. Draws for another strong showing. OUR ROKU (4) returns to the front line and won here the last time she started on this line.",
